<br>
If mages need anything it is some personal self buffs that reflect the elements that we can control. We get a damage shield with +45sv fire. As it stands our self buffing is horrid. Just about every other casting class can self buff better then a mage. Even the hybrids can self buff better then we can.  I personally think mages being the elementalist in the game, and having a strong control over earth should be able to self hitpoint buff themselves higher then any other casting class in the game. I mean we have no defense some extra hps would be nice.<br>
