<br>
Not every 60  mage is in an ubber guild doing PoP. The spell could be useful for: faction, farming of trade components, clearing area to a boss mob(not in PoP), etc.<br>
<br>
Not everyone level at the same pace. Many guilds have players on a wide range of levels. Sure I might not get xp outside of PoP but that should not be a deterrent to helping a friend get upgrades in another non-PoP zone. <br>
